commit.message: No appveyor tests until I figured out what goes wrong.
Remove appveyor
Remove appveyor
No appveyor tests until I figured out what goes wrong.
No appveyor tests until I figured out what goes wrong.
Fix nbextension tab disappearing
Load jQuery instead of jQueryUI only when require('jquery-ui') === undef
Change loaded module from jQueryUI to jQuery
remove py3.3 tests which will not work with notebook>5.2
update appveyor config to use pip as a module

add _jupyter_nbextension_paths, allows jupyter nbextension install

This matters because there is no way for jupyter nbextension list to 
know that jupyter_nbextensions_configurator is going to add it's static 
file path at runtime. If you can't install it explicitly into the 
jupyter data files directories there is no way for that validation to 
succeed.
Remove more tests in travis
Remove check
Remove tests for Python 3 until it is clear why they are failing
